content.description: Many ways to start this problem. Moves through two pairs of crimps with an exciting pop to a large, course pocket on the lip. Sharp and fun.
content.location: On the south face of the boulder next to Monkey Skull.

content.description: Begin next to (right of) the ocotillo on south side of boulder adjacent to Monkey Skull. Perhaps calling this boulder the Monkey Butt would be logical...   Anyrate, Start on two good edges, then go up with left to a 2finger-pocket. Find another 2finger pocket for right hand and then up to yet another pocket.  Trend up and right thru knobs/cobbles to big ledge.  Down climb arete like feature at walkthrough next to Monkey Skull on NE side of boulder.
content.location: East arete area of Monkey Butt (Boulder next to south of Monkey Skull)

content.description: Sit start. Throw to a left hand pinch on the arete, find the beautiful right hand undercling. Use high friction slopers or small crimps on the top. Worth doing just for the undercling.
content.location: West arete of the boulder just south of/next to the Monkey Skull

content.description: Starts low on the arete right of Curious George. Moves up the bulge using the holds near the lip, including two baseball-sized cobbles. Staying lower on the lip makes it harder. Tops out to the right of Curious George.
content.location: Start on arete right of Curious George.

content.description: Starting matched on a big watermelon sized cobble real low under the bulge, climb through crimps, cobbles through the steepest part of the boulder. The lip and headwall have good holds, but is still kinda tricky.
Start matched on large block, go right to a two finger pocket. Heel the block and cross to the big pocket. Move up the face to the left of Curious George
content.location: Just to the left of Curious George, left side of the Monkey Skull boulder

content.description: A little bit downhill from the Beast are two boulders with a little chimney between them. The left boulder has an obvious overhanging bulge, and from a distance looks like a monkey skull.
